Singer Naira Marley has advised ladies on how best to achieve long-lasting relationships. The “First Time in America” singer, who is known to have one of the most controversial fanbase, in a recent tweet said ladies should endeavour to regularly source other females for their boyfriends. According to the Marlian president, by so doing, their relationship will last longer. “Try to dey give your boyfriend babes so the relationship go last longer”, he tweeted. Reacting to Naira Marley’s supposed tip to achieving a long-lasting relationship, a good number of social media users said the gesture should be vice versa. - Advertisement - Others said the singer is very well known for dishing out absurd advice. elmannygram stated: “Naira Marley and bad advice na 5&6.” cruise_lanje_nation said: “This one dey drop bad advice pass hit.”   I’ll treat illegal refinery operators worse than Boko Haram…     Outrage as three teenagers slaughter, burn girlfriend’s…     PHOTOS: Suspended DCP Abba Kyari makes first public…   wendy_adammma wrote: “Same goes to the men too.” callmedamy stated: “Werey ni president wa.” shes_spotless asked: “Which kind format be this na?” thekayinsola said: “As long as he can also give me guys. I’m sure he knows my spec.” keepinghealthy.sexlife wrote: “Nothing we dis guy de ever talk de make sense….kunu brain.” jhoygurl stated: “Make our boyfriends try dey give us other guys too since everybody is running mad.” omabarbie1 asked: “The bf go de give his babe guy also? Asking for my neighbour.” dr_bills said: “This one is not normal.” ushersinnigeria wrote: “Wasn’t expecting much from him.” estradas_ignacious stated: “Vive versa…I give u, u give me. Everybody is happy.”